1
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:10,240
Brother

2
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,000
What's going on, exactly?

3
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,560
After you left that day,

4
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,600
I stayed guarding the jungle entrance.

5
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,680
Later, I don't know why,

6
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:19,880
Hong Ye showed up.

7
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,560
We chatted a bit, too.

8
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,880
What's the problem?

9
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,720
So those videos were real.

10
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,560
You were trying to kill Wudi.

11
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,000
He's not Zhao Wudi.

12
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,520
Wudi died a long time ago.

13
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,200
He's a fake.

14
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,320
If he really were Zhao Wudi,

15
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,840
would he do something like this?

16
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:45,960
He's not the Zhao Wudi you

17
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,960
can't stop thinking about.

18
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:52,840
Xingyu.

19
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,040
You should know that.

20
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,040
I had amnesia back then.

21
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,120
And what I did with her

22
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,280
was for a reason.

23
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:01,200
Stop using amnesia as an excuse.

24
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,880
Does amnesia justify your partying?

25
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,920
You're messing around with these women.

26
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,640
You don't deserve to be with my sister.

27
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,960
Xingyu, let me explain.

28
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,400
Enough. You don't have to explain.

29
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,000
I trust my brother.

30
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,080
Brother Wudi,

31
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,960
there's gotta be some misunderstanding.

32
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,920
You and Brother Xingchen were so close,

33
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,400
comrades-in-arms and like family.

34
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,160
He...

35
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,840
How did he end up like this?

36
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,120
Lao Liu.

37
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,160
You didn't notice Brother Xingchen

38
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,640
was acting kind of off?

39
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,160
Something did feel off.

40
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,000
Could it be Brother Xingchen

41
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,760
is really the mastermind?

42
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,240
Now that Hong Ye is dead,

43
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,040
he decided to stop pretending.

44
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,040
Maybe.

45
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,440
But at least

46
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,400
he's Xingyu's own brother.

47
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,320
Xingyu will be fine.

48
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,040
True.

49
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,160
Then we'll investigate it slowly.

50
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,080
Brother Wudi,

51
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,920
Liu will always be your good brother.

52
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,400
Liu,

53
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,680
you're my best brother.

54
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:32,960
We're brothers.

55
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,960
Why are you being polite with me?

56
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,440
Little brother...

57
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:39,600
Little brother...

58
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,480
You really beat Hong Ye.

59
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,080
That's amazing!

60
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,800
That's badass!

61
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,800
But you got stabbed in the back by a

62
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,080
trusted comrade.

63
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,920
What happened?

64
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,680
Even though Hong Ye is dead,

65
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,080
Dawa and

66
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,000
Sister Fei

67
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:54,800
have already escaped.

68
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,480
I suspect

69
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,160
Shen Xingchen

70
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,560
is the mastermind behind it all.

71
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,200
One crisis after another.

72
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,440
So what's your plan next?

73
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,080
Keep digging.

74
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,640
If it really is him,

75
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,680
I'm not letting him get away with it.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,000
Okay. I support you.

77
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,840
I support you.

78
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,800
If you ever need anything,

79
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,640
just let me know.

80
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,720
Thanks, boss.

81
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,800
But as for the trading company,

82
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,120
you won't be going back there anymore.

83
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:21,320
From now on, you live here.

84
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,800
Stay as long as you want.

85
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,120
Go easy on the drinks, alright?

86
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:27,920
I've gotta get back to work.

87
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,000
Dongba is completely in chaos now.

88
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,560
We've achieved our goal.

89
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,000
If we step in now

90
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,240
and take control of the aftermath,

91
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,800
within a month,

92
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,920
we can unify Dongba.

93
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,720
Unify?

94
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,480
How do we unify it?

95
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,920
You think they'll just sit there

96
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,920
and let you unify it?

97
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,280
I've got a list of names.

98
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,160
We'll go find them one by one.

99
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,600
They either submit to me,

100
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:56,800
or

101
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,200
they can go keep Hong Ye company in hell.

102
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,040
They don't get a choice.

103
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,840
Under Dawa,

104
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,640
there are still many of Hong Ye's loyal men.

105
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,480
You think

106
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,440
he'll just let you take them?

107
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,800
And Sister Fei.

108
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,400
She's got plenty of trusted people too.

109
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,880
You think she'll let you take them as well?

110
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,040
I've said it before.

111
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,680
We have to be cautious.

112
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,920
Hong Ye is the cicada.

113
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,320
We won't be the mantis.

114
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,040
We'll be the oriole.

115
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,200
Long time no see, President Shen.

116
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,720
It's you.

117
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,440
What are you doing here?

118
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,720
All for my Zhao Wudi, of course.

119
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,040
Come with me.

120
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,520
Xingyu!

121
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,280
Xingyu, where are you?

122
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:53,640
Wudi!

123
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,520
Wudi!

124
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:55,920
Help me, Wudi!

125
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,560
A Li.

126
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:58,920
Don't do anything stupid.

127
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,080
If you wanna save her,

128
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,560
come to the company.

129
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:02,640
You just wait.

130
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,600
Shen Xingchen's making his move.

131
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,680
I'll go see this show for myself.

132
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,480
Zhao Wudi.

133
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,000
Miss me?

134
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,640
A Li...

135
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,360
What are you up to now?

136
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,720
If I didn't use Shen Xingyu,

137
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,240
would you come see me?

138
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,440
Xingyu.

139
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:48,960
Don't be afraid.

140
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,520
A Li,

141
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,000
Your trip to Dongba this time

142
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,480
wasn't just to save some rich man's kid,

143
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,640
was it?

144
00:06:57,960 --> 00:07:00,160
Going undercover next to Dawa for so long...

145
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,240
Who's pulling your strings?

146
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,920
Trying to seize Hong Ye's forces?

147
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,800
That's the man I fell for.

148
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,720
Right on the mark.

149
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,880
That's right.

150
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,000
I was acting on someone's orders.

151
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,560
That person...

152
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,800
You know him too.

153
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,000
Zhao Wudi.

154
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,440
Looks like to deal with you...

155
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,080
my sister is still the most useful.

156
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,480
Shen Xingchen, are you insane?

157
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,360
She's your own sister!

158
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,920
You're using your own sister to blackmail me?

159
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,280
Let me tell you.

160
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,440
If I can take you down today,

161
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,720
I'd tie up my own mother.

162
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,640
After hiding for so long,

163
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,120
talk.

164
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,280
What's your real goal?

165
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,160
I want all of Dongba.

166
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,400
I want to control everything.

167
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,840
Snap out of it!

168
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:17,080
You're not yourself anymore.

169
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,920
Someone's controlling you.

170
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,760
Do you get it?

171
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,720
Are you kidding me?

172
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,840
Who could control me?

173
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,720
Back then...

174
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,480
Back then, into your brain,

175
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,960
they implanted the Wushuang chip.

176
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,000
You became someone else's puppet.

177
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,440
Even though the chip has been removed,

178
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,480
you never fully recovered.

179
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,520
Right now, Brother Xingchen,

180
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,600
your mind must be under someone's control.

181
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,440
That's why you did so much evil.

182
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,520
Bullshit.

183
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,200
I'm telling you,

184
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,080
nobody can control me.

185
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,520
Except me.

186
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,760
Look at her.

187
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,960
Look at Xingyu.

188
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,160
Don't you remember?

189
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,120
She's the sister you loved most.

190
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,440
You used to do anything for her.

191
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:01,160
You'd even die for her.

192
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,240
Brother.

193
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,640
Brother!

194
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,040
It's you.

195
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,560
It has to be you!

196
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,400
You're the one messing with my head!

197
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,680
I'm killing you today!

198
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:07,800
Zhao Wudi!

199
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:08,920
You can't die!

200
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,440
Zhao Wudi, get up!

201
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:11,880
Zhao Wudi!

202
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,680
Zhao Wudi!

203
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,680
I searched high and low,

204
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,480
only for it to fall right into my lap.

205
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,440
I never expected it.

206
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,120
Zhao Wudi.

207
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,520
Shen Xingchen.

208
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,880
For two such tough opponents...

209
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:33,520
to actually...

210
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,880
take each other out just like this.

211
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,480
Boss.

212
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,240
What do you mean by that?

213
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,720
Actually,

214
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,840
Shen Xingchen

215
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,320
was controlled by me.

216
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,480
Impossible.

217
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,560
I've got Wushuang right here.

218
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,240
Impossible!

219
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,440
No one...

220
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,600
No one can...

221
00:10:58,760 --> 00:10:59,600
control me.

222
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,840
Kill Zhao Wudi.

223
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,640
You're useless now.

224
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,160
Once my men

225
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,240
kill Sister Fei and Dawa,

226
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,520
those two idiots,

227
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,560
all of Dongba

228
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:15,160
will be mine.

229
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:15,960
Master!

230
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:18,720
Master!

231
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,160
What's wrong?

232
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:29,520
Boss...

233
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,760
To think you were the mastermind.

234
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:36,760
Zhao Wudi.

235
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,600
I'm just taking back what's mine.

236
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:43,760
I'd given up back then.

237
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,880
But then I met you.

238
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,880
The top expert on the Gray List.

239
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,120
I knew it.

240
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,880
Heaven sent you to help me.

241
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,200
So I took you in.

242
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:59,000
You truly were a great pawn.

243
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,160
Such a pity.

244
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,120
You're about to die.

245
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,400
But I should thank you.

246
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,760
Boss...

247
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:15,080
You finally admitted it yourself.

248
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:23,040
So you two were playing dead.

249
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,200
If we didn't,

250
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,840
how else would you expose yourself?

251
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,480
Nida!

252
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,800
Go save Xingyu, now!

253
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,040
Boss.

254
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,720
We knew there was a hidden force

255
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,800
that was bought by an overseas syndicate

256
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:39,840
to eliminate me.

257
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,400
For Xingyu's safety,

258
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:42,800
I went alone to lure the enemy out.

259
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,360
Sure enough,

260
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,040
you all came out in force.

261
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:47,680
The plan was perfect.

262
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,600
But it's a shame.

263
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,000
You didn't kill me.

264
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,200
I only temporarily

265
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,680
lost my memory.

266
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:57,000
You're lying to me.

267
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,720
So you didn't lose your memory.

268
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:01,840
Wudi wanted to expose the mastermind himself.

269
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:03,320
Once he knew they were in Dongba,

270
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,800
he came here to find them.

271
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:05,800
And me,

272
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,640
I used a pager

273
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,720
to coordinate with him.

274
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,560
(Stay at the No-Name Restaurant)

275
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,240
Boss,

276
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,160
I got my memory back a long time ago.

277
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,960
Just to smoke you out,

278
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,360
I pretended to still have amnesia.

279
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,040
When Brother Xingchen came this time,

280
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,120
we put on

281
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:29,160
a show of brothers killing each other

282
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:31,760
just to lure you out.

283
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:32,920
You used me

284
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,920
to go after Hong Ye and Sister Fei,

285
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,920
trying to seize Dongba for yourself.

286
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,920
Now watch how I deal with you.

287
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,320
Brilliant.

288
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,680
Absolutely brilliant.

289
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,760
Truly spectacular.

290
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,600
I really didn't expect

291
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,680
you'd meticulously planned

292
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,800
such an elaborate show.

293
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,960
just for me.

294
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,640
But you didn't stop to think

295
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,760
why I came alone.

296
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,720
I came exactly to watch you put on this show.

297
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:03,920
While you were acting,

298
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,080
my men

299
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:07,440
already took over Hong Ye and Sister Fei's turf,

300
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,920
every last bit of it.

301
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,600
Now Dongba

302
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,960
is mine.

303
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,800
Dongba doesn't mean shit.

304
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,520
I'm telling you,

305
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:17,520
once we take you down today,

306
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:19,480
owning the whole world won't save you.

307
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,680
Yeah.

308
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,240
Yeah.

309
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,040
How could I forget?

310
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,960
You two are that tough.

311
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,960
Why wouldn't I leave myself

312
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,600
a backup plan?
